This script is running under the SLURM workload manager. It utilizes several software packages like Anaconda3, CUDA, Python, and a custom library Texpose. The script also requires various hardware resources like CPU, GPU, and disk space for data storage and processing. The script performs tasks like model training, evaluation, and rendering of 3D objects.
